name: Book Bundles
description:
These bundles are a perfect accessory and add height where needed!
They add much needed height on side tables, book shelves, ect.
These would also make great centerpieces!

Each bundle comes with three books, but sizes vary.
They are available in an aged light wash and an aged dark wax.
Choose which one you like best!
We only glue down the top pages and the back pages, the rest stays readable!


We most certainly do bulk orders, just message me in advance! We will also do combined shipping!

Message me for any inquiries! :]

name: Burlap Wreaths
description:
Hi!

We specialize in burlap wreaths that can be used throughout the year! They are available in the oatmeal/ blonde color and the natural burlap color. 

 Every wreath is created with 6" ribbon to ensure fullness!

**If you would like a bow added to your wreath, please specify in the notes section!** (no additional costs!)

If you have an questions please ask prior to purchasing!

Thanks so much!
Bethany
